title: Love this game
text: This game is so fun and I play it when I don’t have anything else to do, but one thing that bothers me is that some of the characters cost money. There was this one character, I forgot her name, and my friend showed me it and when I finally got my own phone I wanted her so bad. I found out that she costed like, 4 or 5 dollars, and I would not wan tot spend that much on a character. I might if it was 1 or 2 dollars, but I feel like they are overpriced and unreasonably “expensive” for a game. Other than that though, I loved this game and would give it a 5 star if it wasn’t for that one thing with the characters. Thank you! Have a nice day! 🐷

title: AMAAAAZIING(but a few things)
text:
So I have been playing this game for a very long time now and It’s the best endless running game EVER. But however I have a few requests. First of all, the plant invasion is so fun and tough, love that but not this: It takes forever to complete–you’d have to play like 2-3 hours straight to do it and I can only barely complete the 1st of 5 stages in just under an hour so It would be great if you guys could shorten it a bit. Next, instead of having to get the sticker pack separately that would be nice if you would get the stickers with the app. Last of all, make the seasons like 1-3 weeks longer than usual. Otherwise, I can’t think of anything better to add to the app, so AMAZING job on the game and consider some of those things. 

Sincerely, LongShotHawk

Ps: also guys, if you are going to respond to people don’t just copy and paste your responses and that’s just not nice to do so PLEASE actually write your responses devs.
